Finally someone has a Gothic Jukebox





The pupose of this page is to give the gothic community of Denver a place on the web where
one may feel free to meet other people, read about them and as well come together and plan
social events...etc. I don't know about you but it is not easy to find a place where goth's
can go and hang out with other goth's. There used to be a few happening places but everyone seems to be 
dissapearing. Perhaps everyone is getting bored of going to clubs where half the people
there are a bunch of yuppies who just want to check out "The freak show" "eh"?
Well we need to think about somewhere and something for us. Somewhere we can be comfortable.
 So in this I present to you This website. No advertising...
No profit...I'm doing this cause I Love you guy's and gals. I feel at home when I am with you.
But this page will not be a success without you. Actually You are exactly what this page needs
to exsist. I need all your ideas, poetry, pictures, art, plans, meeting places, party's, and anything
else that you can think of to give to other goth's here in denver.
